2. ğŸ“¦ REQUIRED PLUGINS:
   - Pipeline Plugin
   - Credentials Plugin  
   - HTML Publisher Plugin (for reports)
   - Email Extension Plugin (for notifications)
   - Slack Notification Plugin (optional)

